com.instagram.mainactivity.InstagramMain: This activity involves managing user profiles and interactions, creating and editing content, exploring media, and adjusting privacy and notification settings on a social media platform.
com.instagram.modal.ModalActivity: The activity facilitates Instagram account login, reel post, and editing cover options for highlights.
com.instagram.modal.TransparentModalActi: The activity allows users to interact with story by browsing, liking, sharing stories, creating highlights, accessing more options.
ui0: The activity facilitates user log-out by prompting confirmation, offering options to cancel or interact with content, and enabling dialog closure without action.
